Bundled font (Ideographic Description Characters fallback):

public/apps/rare-glyph/fonts/BabelStoneHan-IDC-subset.woff2 — a modified
subset (only U+2FF0–U+2FFF and U+31EF) of BabelStone Han by Andrew West,
itself derived from the Arphic (文鼎) AR PL fonts. Licensed under the
ARPHIC PUBLIC LICENSE — see public/apps/rare-glyph/fonts/ARPHIC_PUBLIC_LICENSE.txt.
This subset is a modified version produced with fontTools/pyftsubset; the
copyright and license notices are retained in the font's name table.
Upstream: https://www.babelstone.co.uk/Fonts/Han.html
  (c) Copyright 1994-1999, Arphic Technology Co., Ltd.
  (c) Copyright 2009-2025, Andrew West.
